title: NFL ATL: Who are first-ballot HOF locks?
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Who are first-ballot HOF locks?
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling -- break down the latest news, including Marshawn Lynch's belated arrival at Seahawks camp. The guys also debate which active NFL players are first-ballot locks for the Pro Football Hall of Fame.
